<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>You're now the Owner of {{ teamName }}</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #f4f4f5; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;">
    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background: #f4f4f5; padding: 32px 16px;">
        <tr>
            <td align="center">
                <table width="560" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.08);">
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 24px 32px; background: #0f766e;">
                            <h1 style="margin: 0; color: #fff; font-size: 20px;">You're now the Owner of {{ teamName }}</h1>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 32px; font-size: 15px; color: #3f3f46; line-height: 1.6;">
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0;">
                                <strong>{{ previousOwnerEmail }}</strong> transferred ownership of the Sendvery team <strong>{{ teamName }}</strong> to you.
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; color: #71717a;">
                                As Owner you can invite or remove teammates, change roles, transfer ownership again, and adjust team settings. {{ previousOwnerEmail }} is now an Admin on the team — they keep elevated rights but can't transfer ownership.
                            </p>
                            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;">
                                <a href="{{ teamSettingsUrl }}" style="display: inline-block; padding: 14px 36px; background: #0f766e; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600;">
                                    Manage the team
                                </a>
                            </div>
                            <p style="margin: 16px 0 0 0; font-size: 13px; color: #a1a1aa;">
                                If you weren't expecting this transfer, reach out to {{ previousOwnerEmail }} to sort it out — they triggered the change.
                            </p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>
